'''Adam Warren''' was the cover artist for ''[[Star Wars Manga: A New Hope]]'', ''[[Star Wars Manga: The Empire Strikes Back]]'' and ''[[Star Wars Manga: Return of the Jedi]]''. For the project he used a combination of digital and traditional media.

